{"tid":2139414,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人大左，發現矮嘅男仔好似一世乞求人嘅認同咁","createTime":"2020-08-04T09:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T14:14:09.000Z","uid":71508,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"dd22e29ad4360f36d3bfa1cf842a2321ea5f63c5","tid":2139414,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"到自己做左大人至知<br />\n原來人真係睇樣<br />\n原來身高真係好影響人地對你觀感<br />\n矮個d男仔<br />\n好似無論做咩都俾人笑<br />\nd女又當佢地唔係人<br />\n同埋有樣野一定要講<br />\n依個社會<br />\n太迷信努力<br />\nd人成日以為<br />\n佢地同其他人既分別同距離<br />\n只係在於佢地唔夠努力<br />\n其實好想講<br />\n你生得夠高大<br />\n六呎一二吋個d<br />\nd女真係可以無視你缺點<br />\n或者咁講<br />\n缺點都講成優點<br />\n或者再咁講<br />\n所謂優缺點<br />\n只係一個人<br />\n對你鍾意定嫌棄既說辭<br />\n男人生得矮<br />\n好似無時無刻<br />\n都響度證明緊d咩咁"},{"pid":"4a2cdfa516ec7c6c42f7d7da9f78e288892b8b94","tid":2139414,"uid":266336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"梳9ly囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a77750de3f1937b95eaee8d87582c317a5a0df","tid":2139414,"uid":147916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"係咁㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f0df0d73eed086c9e2bb544af3f964e9f935a2","tid":2139414,"uid":211074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32f1ea47e65a8c9b64661dba10d34afe653b9f5","tid":2139414,"uid":89546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f01bda7cc767bd5e3f0bd69b7557a3d8c365ee","tid":2139414,"uid":139244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:18:09.000Z","msg":"真，唔夠180都算係矮撚<br />\n利申：181"},{"pid":"1d719253984f58d6fc94275943de8c7f2ed77fc5","tid":2139414,"uid":28626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r